{"tid":360313,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【林子健全體撞車】黃絲豬進入庫伯勒-羅絲心理學模型第1階段！","createTime":"2017-08-15T07:55:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-15T15:32:59.000Z","uid":79563,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a89874e75705a7b7a48dfe7c81b003ce1bb4adb8","tid":360313,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T07:55:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s14.postimg.org/tvnmh3xvl/image.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs14.postimg.org%2Ftvnmh3xvl%2Fimage.jpg&h=729c0ced&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n庫伯勒-羅絲模型（K&uuml;bler-Ross model）描述了人對待哀傷與災難過程中的5個獨立階段。絕症患者被認為會經歷這些階段。這一模型是伊莉莎白‧庫伯勒-羅絲在她1969年出版的「論死亡與臨終」（On Death and Dying）一書中提出的。這一模型中的階段後來廣泛流傳，被稱作「哀傷的五個階段」（Five Stages of Grief）。<br />\n<br />\n庫伯勒-羅絲模型五個階段包括：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">「否認」：「不會吧，不可能啊！」</span></span><br />\n「憤怒」：「為什麼是我？這不公平！」「我能怪誰啊？」<br />\n「討價還價」：「讓我活著看到我的兒子畢業就好。求你（祢）了，再給我幾年時間吧！」「如果她能醒來，我什麼都願意做。」<br />\n「抑鬱」：「唉，幹嘛還要管這些事啊？反正我都要死了。」「我不想活了，活著還有什麼意義。」<br />\n「接受」：「好吧！既然我已經沒法改變這件事了，我就好好準備後事吧！」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n 黃絲豬何時會完成5個階段？"},{"pid":"8ca3ec23f04c5f563d739eaa35d441465223e38a","tid":360313,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T08:25:16.000Z","msg":"黃絲豬加油！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85e411c1368aa3d2f6312eba161c4a5d7ae716cf","tid":360313,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T15:18:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5de19fc0063ffe